So a dev I know advised me to think outside of the box and use the search api, <@U02LTUSGLE9>!

You can use the CRM Search API and just send an empty object `{}` for a “search” of everything. The response body has a `total` field.

For contacts it would be POST `crm/v3/objects/contacts/search`
```{}```
And the response would look like
```{
  "total": 409,
  "results": [
...
  ],
  "paging": {
    "next": {
      "after": "10"
    }
  }
}```
